      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study performed on FDA pump geometry at 5 L/min, 3500 RPM operating point. Coarse (2.1M), medium (5.8M), and fine (14.2M) cell counts yielded GCI of 3.7% on normalized index of hemolysis. Gradation 2 achieved."
