      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) must agree with experimental measurements within 15% across all five operating points at Gradation 2.",
      "rationale": "Predicted RH values compared against FDA experimental data across 5 operating points. Mean absolute error of 8.3%, maximum deviation 13.1% at 3 L/min, 3500 RPM. All five points within the 15% acceptance band. Gradation 2 achieved."
